	(13, NULL, 'id', 'BOC, BOD and Member of Organization', 1, '<div class="row section"><div class="col-sm-12"><div class="type"><div class="text-wrapper cke_editable cke_editable_inline cke_contents_ltr cke_show_borders" id="editor2" spellcheck="false" style="position: relative;" role="textbox" aria-label="Rich Text Editor, editor2" title="Rich Text Editor, editor2" aria-describedby="cke_147" contenteditable="false"><p style="text-align:center"><strong>BOARD OF COMMISSIONERS</strong></p></div></div></div></div><div class="row section"><div class="col-sm-12"><div class="type"><div class="text-wrapper cke_editable cke_editable_inline cke_contents_ltr cke_focus cke_show_borders" id="editor3" spellcheck="false" style="position: relative;" role="textbox" aria-label="Rich Text Editor, editor3" title="Rich Text Editor, editor3" aria-describedby="cke_198" contenteditable="false"><p style="text-align:center"><img alt="" data-cke-saved-src="/kcfinder/upload/images/2020/GEDE%20PASEK%20SUARDIKA.jpg" src="/kcfinder/upload/images/2020/GEDE%20PASEK%20SUARDIKA.jpg" style="height:200px; width:178px"></p><p style="text-align:center">Dr. GEDE PASEK SUARDIKA, M.Sc</p></div></div></div></div><div class="row section"><div class="col-sm-12"><div class="type"><div class="text-wrapper cke_editable cke_editable_inline cke_contents_ltr cke_show_borders" id="editor4" spellcheck="false" style="position: relative;" role="textbox" aria-label="Rich Text Editor, editor4" title="Rich Text Editor, editor4" aria-describedby="cke_249" contenteditable="false"><p style="text-align:justify">Officially appointed as the Executive Commissioner of PT INKA (Persero) since March 2020. He graduated from the University of Leeds, United Kingdom, with a major in Transportation in 1988 and a Doctorate at Tarumanegara University with a major in Civil Engineering in 2013. He currently serves as General Inspector of the Ministry of Transportation. &nbsp;The awards he had received were Satya Lancana Karya Satya 10 Years in 2000 and Satya Lancana Karya Satya 20 Years in 2009.</p></div></div></div></div><div class="row section"><div class="col-sm-4"><div class="type"><div class="text-wrapper cke_editable cke_editable_inline cke_contents_ltr cke_show_borders" id="editor5" spellcheck="false" style="position: relative;" role="textbox" aria-label="Rich Text Editor, editor5" title="Rich Text Editor, editor5" aria-describedby="cke_300" contenteditable="false"><p style="text-align:center"><img alt="" data-cke-saved-src="/kcfinder/upload/images/2020/M.%20KHAYAM.png.jpg" src="/kcfinder/upload/images/2020/M.%20KHAYAM.png.jpg" style="height:200px; width:136px"></p><p style="text-align:center">Ir. MUHAMMAD KHAYAM, M.T.</p></div></div></div><div class="col-sm-4"><div class="type"><div class="text-wrapper cke_editable cke_editable_inline cke_contents_ltr cke_show_borders" id="editor6" spellcheck="false" style="position: relative;" role="textbox" aria-label="Rich Text Editor, editor6" title="Rich Text Editor, editor6" aria-describedby="cke_351" contenteditable="false"><p style="text-align:center"><img alt="" data-cke-saved-src="/kcfinder/upload/images/2020/Safri.jpg" src="/kcfinder/upload/images/2020/Safri.jpg" style="height:200px; width:150px">​​​​​​​</p><p style="text-align:center">Dr. Ir. SAFRI BURHANUDIN, DEA.</p></div></div></div><div class="col-sm-4"><div class="type"><div class="text-wrapper cke_editable cke_editable_inline cke_contents_ltr cke_show_borders" id="editor7" spellcheck="false" style="position: relative;" role="textbox" aria-label="Rich Text Editor, editor7" title="Rich Text Editor, editor7" aria-describedby="cke_402" contenteditable="false"><p style="text-align:center"><img alt="" data-cke-saved-src="/kcfinder/upload/images/Siti_Malkhamah.png" src="/kcfinder/upload/images/Siti_Malkhamah.png" style="height:200px; width:200px"></p><p style="text-align:center">Prof. Ir. SITI MALKHAMAH, M.Sc., Ph.D.</p></div></div></div></div><div class="row section"><div class="col-sm-4"><div class="type"><div class="text-wrapper cke_editable cke_editable_inline cke_contents_ltr cke_show_borders" id="editor8" spellcheck="false" style="position: relative;" role="textbox" aria-label="Rich Text Editor, editor8" title="Rich Text Editor, editor8" aria-describedby="cke_453" contenteditable="false"><p style="text-align:justify">Officially appointed as Commissioner of PT INKA (Persero) since March 2020. He is a graduate of Chemical Engineering, Bandung Institute of Technology (1990) and continued his education in the Masters Program in Mechanical Engineering at the University of Indonesia (2002). Currently he serves as Director General of Chemical, Pharmaceutical and Textile Industries, Ministry of Industry. He has received several awards, namely Satyalancana Karya Satya X and XX by the President of the Republic of Indonesia in 2001 and 2017.</p></div></div></div><div class="col-sm-4"><div class="type"><div class="text-wrapper cke_editable cke_editable_inline cke_contents_ltr cke_show_borders" id="editor9" spellcheck="false" style="position: relative;" role="textbox" aria-label="Rich Text Editor, editor9" title="Rich Text Editor, editor9" aria-describedby="cke_504" contenteditable="false"><p style="text-align:justify">Officially appointed as the Commissioner of PT INKA (Persero) as of October 2017, he is also the Deputy IV in Human Capital Coordination Subject, Science Technology and Nautical Culture in Coordinator Ministry of Nautical Field Republic of Indonesia. He was born in Ujung Pandang in 1961, he achieved his Bachelor Degree of Geology Subject in Padjajaran University and proceeded to Universitie de Bretagne Occidentale, France in Marine Geology Subject and achieved his degree in 1994.</p></div></div></div><div class="col-sm-4"><div class="type"><div class="text-wrapper cke_editable cke_editable_inline cke_contents_ltr cke_focus cke_show_borders" id="editor10" spellcheck="false" style="position: relative;" role="textbox" aria-label="Rich Text Editor, editor10" title="Rich Text Editor, editor10" aria-describedby="cke_555" contenteditable="false"><p style="text-align:justify">Officially appointed as an Independent Commissioner of PT INKA (Persero) since March 2020. Her educational background are Bachelor of Civil Engineering at Gadjah Mada University, continuing her Postgraduate &nbsp;Doctorate degree in Transport Planning and Engineering at the University of Leeds, United Kingdom. Her activities such as research, community service, scientific publications, seminars and workshops speaker. She has published several books such as "Penggunaan Angkutan Umum untuk Masyarakat Perkotaan" in 2012, “Berbagai Peluang dan Tantangan Yogyakarta” in the 2013 “Buku Bunga Rampai Dewan Riset Daerah DIY” book, “Perkembangan Transportasi dan Kedaulatan Teknologi”in the 2013 “Jati Diri Manusia Indonesia” book; and “Transportasi dan Kesehatan” in the 2015 "Yogyakarta Sehat Lestari" book.</p></div></div></div></div><div class="row section"><div class="col-sm-12"><div class="type"><div class="text-wrapper cke_editable cke_editable_inline cke_contents_ltr cke_show_borders" id="editor11" spellcheck="false" style="position: relative;" role="textbox" aria-label="Rich Text Editor, editor11" title="Rich Text Editor, editor11" aria-describedby="cke_606" contenteditable="false"><p style="text-align:center"><strong>BOARD OF DIRECTORS</strong></p></div></div></div></div><div class="row section"><div class="col-sm-12"><div class="type"><div class="text-wrapper cke_editable cke_editable_inline cke_contents_ltr cke_show_borders" id="editor12" spellcheck="false" style="position: relative;" role="textbox" aria-label="Rich Text Editor, editor12" title="Rich Text Editor, editor12" aria-describedby="cke_657" contenteditable="false"><p style="text-align:center"><img alt="" data-cke-saved-src="/kcfinder/upload/images/2020/Budi%20Noviantoro_(1).jpg" src="/kcfinder/upload/images/2020/Budi%20Noviantoro_(1).jpg" style="height:209px; width:200px"></p><p style="text-align:center">Ir. BUDI NOVIANTORO</p></div></div></div></div><div class="row section"><div class="col-sm-12"><div class="type"><div class="text-wrapper cke_editable cke_editable_inline cke_contents_ltr cke_show_borders" id="editor13" spellcheck="false" style="position: relative;" role="textbox" aria-label="Rich Text Editor, editor13" title="Rich Text Editor, editor13" aria-describedby="cke_708" contenteditable="false"><p style="text-align:justify">Appointed as President Director of PT INKA (Persero) since January 2018. He is a graduate of Civil Engineering. Department of Hydraulics, Sepuluh November Institute of Technology Surabaya in 1985. Previous history of Director of Logistics and Business Development of PT KAI (2014) and Ad Interim President Director of PT KAI (2018).</p></div></div></div></div><div class="row section"><div class="col-sm-4"><div class="type"><div class="text-wrapper cke_editable cke_editable_inline cke_contents_ltr cke_focus cke_show_borders" id="editor14" spellcheck="false" style="position: relative;" role="textbox" aria-label="Rich Text Editor, editor14" title="Rich Text Editor, editor14" aria-describedby="cke_759" contenteditable="false"><p style="text-align:center"><img alt="" data-cke-saved-src="/kcfinder/upload/images/2020/Andy%20Budiman.jpeg" src="/kcfinder/upload/images/2020/Andy%20Budiman.jpeg" style="height:200px; width:184px"></p><p style="text-align:center">ANDY BUDIMAN SE., A.k.</p></div></div></div><div class="col-sm-4"><div class="type"><div class="text-wrapper cke_editable cke_editable_inline cke_contents_ltr cke_show_borders" id="editor15" spellcheck="false" style="position: relative;" role="textbox" aria-label="Rich Text Editor, editor15" title="Rich Text Editor, editor15" aria-describedby="cke_810" contenteditable="false"><p style="text-align:center"><img alt="" data-cke-saved-src="/kcfinder/upload/images/2020/Agung%20Sedaju%20closeup.jpg" src="/kcfinder/upload/images/2020/Agung%20Sedaju%20closeup.jpg" style="height:200px; width:200px"></p><p style="text-align:center">Ir. AGUNG SEDAJU, M.T.</p></div></div></div><div class="col-sm-4"><div class="type"><div class="text-wrapper cke_editable cke_editable_inline cke_contents_ltr cke_show_borders" id="editor16" spellcheck="false" style="position: relative;" role="textbox" aria-label="Rich Text Editor, editor16" title="Rich Text Editor, editor16" aria-describedby="cke_861" contenteditable="false"><p style="text-align:center"><img alt="" data-cke-saved-src="/kcfinder/upload/images/2020/I%20GEDE%20AGUS%20PRAYATNA.jpg" src="/kcfinder/upload/images/2020/I%20GEDE%20AGUS%20PRAYATNA.jpg" style="height:200px; width:132px"></p><p style="text-align:center">I GEDE AGUS PRAYATNA</p></div></div></div></div><div class="row section"><div class="col-sm-4"><div class="type"><div class="text-wrapper cke_editable cke_editable_inline cke_contents_ltr cke_show_borders" id="editor17" spellcheck="false" style="position: relative;" role="textbox" aria-label="Rich Text Editor, editor17" title="Rich Text Editor, editor17" aria-describedby="cke_912" contenteditable="false"><p style="text-align:justify">Appointed as Finance &amp; Human Resources Director of PT INKA (Persero) since March 2020. He started his career as Junior Auditor on the Finance Department of Badan Pengawasan Keuangan dan Pembangunan (BPKP) Joint Team in 1990, Member of Corruption Eradication in 2005-2007, KPK investigator in 2007-2011, as Project Manager PT Sarana Multi Infrastruktur (Persero) Geothermal Project Management Unit in 2016-2018. Finance Director of PT Nindya Beton in 2018-2019 and Associate Director of PT PPA Kapital from June 2019 to March 2020. He is a graduate of University of Indonesia Accounting and D-IV Accountancy at the State College of Accountancy.</p></div></div></div><div class="col-sm-4"><div class="type"><div class="text-wrapper cke_editable cke_editable_inline cke_contents_ltr cke_show_borders" id="editor18" spellcheck="false" style="position: relative;" role="textbox" aria-label="Rich Text Editor, editor18" title="Rich Text Editor, editor18" aria-describedby="cke_963" contenteditable="false"><p style="text-align:justify">Appointed as Development Director of PT INKA (Persero) since January 2018. He holds a Bachelor degree in Bandung Institute of Technology Department of Physical Engineering in 1995 and continued his Master\'s Degree in Engineering at Sepuluh November Institute of Technology Surabaya Department of Electrical Engineering in 2006. He pioneered a career in PT INKA (Persero) since 1996 and served as General Manager of Marketing Division (2011), General Manager of Human Capital Division (2012), General Manager of Logistic Division (2014), and General Manager of Technology Division (2015). He also served as Comissioner of PT INKA Multi Solusi Consulting (2018)</p><p style="text-align:justify"><br></p><p style="text-align:justify"><br></p></div></div></div><div class="col-sm-4"><div class="type"><div class="text-wrapper cke_editable cke_editable_inline cke_contents_ltr cke_show_borders" id="editor19" spellcheck="false" style="position: relative;" role="textbox" aria-label="Rich Text Editor, editor19" title="Rich Text Editor, editor19" aria-describedby="cke_1014" contenteditable="false"><p style="text-align:justify">Appointed as Director of Operation of PT INKA (Persero) since March 2020. He began his career as an employee of PT INKA (Persero) at the Technology Center in 1993, as Head of Project Engineering in 1998, Assistant Manager of Commercial and Technology Division in 2004, Manager of the Private Marketing Department and Exports in 2008, General Manager of Railroad Marketing from 2013 to 2018 and Managing Director of PT INKA Multi Solusi Trading from January 2018 to March 2020. He graduated from Mechanical Engineering at Udayana University in 1992.</p></div></div></div></div>\r\n		    <div class="row section"><div class="col-sm-12"><div class="type"><div class="text-wrapper cke_editable cke_editable_inline cke_contents_ltr cke_show_borders" id="editor20" spellcheck="false" style="position: relative;" role="textbox" aria-label="Rich Text Editor, editor20" title="Rich Text Editor, editor20" aria-describedby="cke_1065" contenteditable="false"><p style="text-align:center"><strong>CORPORATE MEMBERS</strong></p></div></div></div></div>\r\n		    <div class="row section"><div class="col-sm-6"><div class="type"><div class="text-wrapper cke_editable cke_editable_inline cke_contents_ltr cke_show_borders" id="editor21" spellcheck="false" style="position: relative;" role="textbox" aria-label="Rich Text Editor, editor21" title="Rich Text Editor, editor21" aria-describedby="cke_1116" contenteditable="false"><p style="text-align:center">​​​​​​​<img alt="" data-cke-saved-src="/kcfinder/upload/images/2020/P.jpg" src="/kcfinder/upload/images/2020/P.jpg" style="height:169px; width:300px"></p><p style="text-align:center">Ir. PUGUH DWI TJAHJONO</p></div></div></div><div class="col-sm-6"><div class="type"><div class="text-wrapper cke_editable cke_editable_inline cke_contents_ltr cke_show_borders" id="editor22" spellcheck="false" style="position: relative;" role="textbox" aria-label="Rich Text Editor, editor22" title="Rich Text Editor, editor22" aria-describedby="cke_1167" contenteditable="false"><p style="text-align:center"><img alt="" data-cke-saved-src="/kcfinder/upload/images/2020/M.jpg" src="/kcfinder/upload/images/2020/M.jpg" style="height:169px; width:300px"></p><p style="text-align:center">SARMIATUN, MM., CA.</p></div></div></div></div><div class="row section"><div class="col-sm-6"><div class="type"><div class="text-wrapper cke_editable cke_editable_inline cke_contents_ltr cke_focus cke_show_borders" id="editor24" spellcheck="false" style="position: relative;" role="textbox" aria-label="Rich Text Editor, editor24" title="Rich Text Editor, editor24" aria-describedby="cke_1269" contenteditable="false"><p style="text-align:justify">Appointed as General Manager of Corporate Secretary of PT INKA (Persero) since February 2019. He graduated from Mechanical Engineering, Sepuluh November Institute of Technology Surabaya in 1997. He pioneered career at PT INKA (Persero) since 1999 which previously served as General Manager Human Capital in 2017 and as President Director of PT INKA Multi Solution (Subsidiary of PT INKA) Ad Interim in 2018.</p><p><br></p></div></div></div><div class="col-sm-6"><div class="type"><div class="text-wrapper cke_editable cke_editable_inline cke_contents_ltr cke_show_borders" id="editor23" spellcheck="false" style="position: relative;" role="textbox" aria-label="Rich Text Editor, editor23" title="Rich Text Editor, editor23" aria-describedby="cke_1218" contenteditable="false"><p style="text-align:justify">Appointed as General Manager of Internal Audit of PT INKA (Persero) since July 2017. She graduated from Accounting of Brawijaya University and continued her Master\'s Degree in Economics and Business at Gajah Mada University. She started a career in PT INKA (Persero) since 1992.</p></div></div></div></div>', 25, 0, 3, '2020-06-19 09:29:28', '2018-01-05 04:12:58', '2020-06-19 09:36:37', NULL),
	(14, 13, 'id', 'BOD/BOC', 2, NULL, 1, 0, NULL, NULL, '2018-01-05 04:14:38', '2018-01-05 04:15:32', '2018-01-05 04:15:32'),
	(15, 13, 'id', 'BOD / BOC', 0, '<div class="row section"><div class="col-sm-12"><div class="type"><div class="text-wrapper cke_editable cke_editable_inline cke_contents_ltr cke_show_borders" id="editor2" spellcheck="false" style="position: relative;" role="textbox" aria-label="Rich Text Editor, editor2" title="Rich Text Editor, editor2" aria-describedby="cke_79" contenteditable="false"><p style="text-align:center"><strong>DEWAN KOMISARIS</strong></p></div></div></div></div><div class="row section"><div class="col-sm-4"><div class="type"><div class="text-wrapper cke_editable cke_editable_inline cke_contents_ltr cke_show_borders" id="editor3" spellcheck="false" style="position: relative;" role="textbox" aria-label="Rich Text Editor, editor3" title="Rich Text Editor, editor3" aria-describedby="cke_130" contenteditable="false"><p>Dr. Harris Munandar N, M.A.</p><p><br></p><p style="text-align:justify">Menjabat sebagai Komisaris Utama PT INKA (Persero) mulai Oktober 2017, beliau saat ini juga menjabat sebagai Sekretaris Jenderal Kementerian Perindustrian. Lahir di Lampung tahun 1959, Meraih Sarjana Administrasi Negara tahun 1989 di STIA LAN RI, Magister Graduate School of International Development Studies tahun 1996 di Nagoya University dan Doktoral Ph.D bidang International Cooperation Studies tahun 2000 dari Nagoya University.</p></div></div></div><div class="col-sm-4"><div class="type"><div class="text-wrapper cke_editable cke_editable_inline cke_contents_ltr cke_show_borders" id="editor4" spellcheck="false" style="position: relative;" role="textbox" aria-label="Rich Text Editor, editor4" title="Rich Text Editor, editor4" aria-describedby="cke_181" contenteditable="false"><p>Ir. Brahmantio Isdijoso, M.S.</p><p><br></p><p style="text-align:justify">Menjabat sebagai Komisaris PT INKA (Persero) mulai Oktober 2017, saat ini beliau juga sedang menjabat sebagai Direktur Pengelolaan Risiko Keuangan Negara Kementerian Keuangan sejak tanggal 2 April 2015 dimana sebelumnya pernah menjabat sebagai Kepala Bidang Pengelolaan Risiko Fiskal. Lahir di Malang tahun 1965, beliau mendapatkan gelar Master Degree in Agriculture Economics dari Institut Pertanian Bogor pada tahun 1990.</p></div></div></div><div class="col-sm-4"><div class="type"><div class="text-wrapper cke_editable cke_editable_inline cke_contents_ltr cke_show_borders" id="editor5" spellcheck="false" style="position: relative;" role="textbox" aria-label="Rich Text Editor, editor5" title="Rich Text Editor, editor5" aria-describedby="cke_232" contenteditable="false"><p>Dr. Ir. Safri Burhanudin, DEA</p><p><br></p><p style="text-align:justify">Menjabat sebagai Komisaris PT INKA (Persero) mulai Oktober 2017, beliau juga aktif sebagai Deputi IV Bidang Koordinasi SDM, IPTEK dan Budaya Maritim Kementerian Koordinator Bidang Kemaritiman Republik Indonesia. Lahir di Ujung Pandang tahun 1961, beliau mendapatkan gelar sarjana Bidang Studi Geologi di Universitas Pajajaran lalu dilanjutkan di Universite de Bretagne Occidentale, Prancis pada Bidang Studi Marine Geology tamat pada tahun 1994.</p></div></div></div></div>\r\n		    <div class="row section"><div class="col-sm-12"><div class="type"><div class="text-wrapper cke_editable cke_editable_inline cke_contents_ltr cke_focus cke_show_borders" id="editor6" spellcheck="false" style="position: relative;" role="textbox" aria-label="Rich Text Editor, editor6" title="Rich Text Editor, editor6" aria-describedby="cke_283" contenteditable="false"><p style="text-align:center"><strong>DEWAN DIREKSI</strong></p></div></div></div></div><div class="row section"><div class="col-sm-12"><div class="type"><div class="text-wrapper cke_editable cke_editable_inline cke_contents_ltr cke_show_borders" id="editor7" spellcheck="false" style="position: relative;" role="textbox" aria-label="Rich Text Editor, editor7" title="Rich Text Editor, editor7" aria-describedby="cke_334" contenteditable="false"><p style="text-align:justify">Menjabat sebagai Direktur SDM dan Keuangan sejak Agustus 2013. Mengawali karir sebagai Auditor di Badan Pengawasan Keuangan dan Pembangunan (BPKP) dan di beberapa BUMN. Lahir di Magetan tahun 1973 dan menyelesaikan pendidikan Magister Akuntansi dan Akuntan dari STAN.</p></div></div></div></div>', 8, 0, 4, NULL, '2018-01-05 04:17:12', '2018-01-10 02:22:05', '2018-01-10 02:22:05'),
	(16, 13, 'id', 'Divisi', 2, '<div class="row section"><div class="col-sm-12"><div class="type"></div></div></div>', 1, 0, NULL, NULL, '2018-01-05 04:18:08', '2018-01-10 02:40:49', '2018-01-10 02:40:49'),
	(17, 13, 'id', 'Struktur Organisasi', 2, '<div class="row section"><div class="col-sm-12"><div class="type"><div class="image-wrapper"><img src="/kcfinder/upload/images/sto%20inka.JPG"><div class="image-caption">Struktur Organisasi PT INKA (Persero)<br></div></div></div></div></div>', 2, 0, NULL, NULL, '2018-01-05 04:18:33', '2018-01-10 02:40:51', '2018-01-10 02:40:51'),
	(18, 18, 'id', 'Anak Perusahaan', 2, '<div class="row section"><div class="col-sm-12"><div class="type"><div class="image-wrapper"><img src="/kcfinder/upload/images/AnakPerusahaan.jpg"><div class="image-caption"><br></div></div></div></div></div><div class="row section"><div class="col-sm-12"><div class="type"><div title="Rich Text Editor, editor4" class="text-wrapper cke_editable cke_editable_inline cke_contents_ltr cke_show_borders" id="editor4" role="textbox" aria-describedby="cke_67" style="position: relative;" spellcheck="false" aria-label="Rich Text Editor, editor4" contenteditable="false"><p><span style="font-size:14px"><span style="font-family:Arial,Helvetica,sans-serif">PT INKA (Persero) mendirikan dua anak perusahaan yaitu <a href="http://inkamultisolusi.co.id/" data-cke-saved-href="http://inkamultisolusi.co.id/"><strong>PT Inka Multi Solusi </strong></a>dan <a href="http://www.rekaindo.net/" data-cke-saved-href="http://www.rekaindo.net/"><strong>PT Rekaindo Global Jasa</strong> </a>(<em>Joint Venture</em>).</span></span></p></div></div></div></div>\r\n		    <div class="row section"><div class="col-sm-12"><div class="type"><div class="image-wrapper"><img src="/kcfinder/upload/images/Logo-IMS3.png"><div class="image-caption"><i>PT Inka Multi Solusi</i></div></div></div></div></div><div class="row section"><div class="col-sm-12"><div class="type"><div title="Rich Text Editor, editor7" class="text-wrapper cke_editable cke_editable_inline cke_contents_ltr cke_show_borders" id="editor7" role="textbox" aria-describedby="cke_118" style="position: relative;" spellcheck="false" aria-label="Rich Text Editor, editor7" contenteditable="false"><p style="text-align:justify"><span style="font-size:14px"><span style="font-family:Arial,Helvetica,sans-serif">PT Inka Multi Solusi Entitas Anak berdomisili di Jalan MT Haryono No. 103, Madiun, Jawa Timur yang mulai beroperasi tahun 2010. Berdasarkan Akta Notaris No. 21 tanggal 18 Februari 2015 oleh Iswi Artati, SH notaris Kota Surabaya dan telah mendapat persetujuan dari Kementrian Hukum dan Hak Asasi Manusia Republik Indonesia Nomor: AHU-0003053.AH.01.02 tanggal 26 Februari 2015 dilakukan perubahan nama perusahaan yang semula PT. Railindo Global Karya diubah menjadi PT Inka Multi Solusi. </span></span></p><p style="text-align:justify"><span style="font-size:14px"><span style="font-family:Arial,Helvetica,sans-serif">Kepemilikan Saham : PT INKA (Persero) 98,93 % dan sisanya Yayasan Keluarga Besar INKA sebesar 1,07%. Kompetensi bisnis yang dimiliki yaitu perdagangan komponen gerbong kereta api, jasa penunjang kereta, jasa fabrikasi, jasa pemasangan, jasa rekayasa (<em>engineering</em>), membuat desain dan melakukan perawatan produk di bidang perkeretaapian serta penyedia jasa tenaga kerja/buruh. Dengan susunan Dewan Komisaris dan Direksi di tahun 2013 adalah sebagai berikut :</span></span></p><table style="height:54px" class=" cke_show_border" border="0" align="left"><tbody><tr><td colspan="3" style="text-align:justify"><span style="font-size:14px"><span style="font-family:Arial,Helvetica,sans-serif"><strong>Dewan Komisaris</strong></span></span></td></tr><tr><td style="text-align:justify"><span style="font-size:14px"><span style="font-family:Arial,Helvetica,sans-serif">Komisaris &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;&nbsp;</span></span></td><td style="text-align:justify"><span style="font-size:14px"><span style="font-family:Arial,Helvetica,sans-serif">:&nbsp;&nbsp; </span></span></td><td style="text-align:justify"><span style="font-size:14px"><span style="font-family:Arial,Helvetica,sans-serif">Mardiannus Pramudya&nbsp;</span></span></td></tr><tr><td style="text-align:justify"><br></td><td style="text-align:justify"><br></td><td style="text-align:justify"><br></td></tr><tr><td style="text-align:justify"><span style="font-size:14px"><span style="font-family:Arial,Helvetica,sans-serif"><strong>Direksi</strong></span></span></td><td style="text-align:justify"><br></td><td style="text-alig