gy Surabaya in 2005. He started his career as General Manager of Finance Division in 2014 and General Manager of &nbsp; Logistic Division in 2018.</p></div></div></div><div class="col-sm-4"><div class="type"><div class="text-wrapper cke_editable cke_editable_inline cke_contents_ltr cke_show_borders" id="editor40" spellcheck="false" style="position: relative;" role="textbox" aria-label="Rich Text Editor, editor40" title="Rich Text Editor, editor40" aria-describedby="cke_413" tabindex="0" ><p><img alt="" data-cke-saved-src="/kcfinder/upload/images/Dirtek.jpg" src="/kcfinder/upload/images/Dirtek.jpg" style="height:169px; width:300px"></p><p style="text-align:center">Ir. AGUNG SEDAJU, M.T.</p><p style="text-align:justify">Appointed as Technology and Commercial Director of PT INKA (Persero) since January 2018. He holds a Bachelor degree of Physical Engineering at Bandung Institute of Technology&nbsp; in 1995 and continued his Master\'s Degree of Electrical Engineering at&nbsp; Sepuluh November Institute of Technology Surabaya in 2006. He pioneered a career in PT INKA (Persero) since 1996 and served as General Manager of Human Capital Division in 2012, General Manager of Logistic Division in 2014, and General Manager of Technology Division <span style="font-size:14px;">in 2015</span>.<br></p></div></div></div><div class="col-sm-4"><div class="type"><div class="text-wrapper cke_editable cke_editable_inline cke_contents_ltr cke_show_borders" id="editor41" spellcheck="false" style="position: relative;" role="textbox" aria-label="Rich Text Editor, editor41" title="Rich Text Editor, editor41" aria-describedby="cke_464" tabindex="0" ><p><img alt="" data-cke-saved-src="/kcfinder/upload/images/Dirprod.jpg" src="/kcfinder/upload/images/Dirprod.jpg" style="height:169px; width:300px"></p><p style="text-align:center">Ir. BAYU WASKITO SUDADI, M.T.</p><p style="text-align:justify">Appointed as Director of Production of PT INKA (Persero) since January 2018. He graduated from&nbsp; Mechanical Engineering at Sepuluh November Institute of Technology Surabaya in 1992 and continued his Master\'s Degree in Mechatronics Engineering at Sepuluh November Institute of Technology Surabaya in 2005. Previous history General Manager of Finishing Division in 2014 and General Manager of Logistics Division in 2015.</p></div></div></div></div><div class="row section"><div class="col-sm-12"><div class="type"><div class="text-wrapper cke_editable cke_editable_inline cke_contents_ltr cke_show_borders" id="editor44" spellcheck="false" style="position: relative;" role="textbox" aria-label="Rich Text Editor, editor44" title="Rich Text Editor, editor44" aria-describedby="cke_617" tabindex="0" ><p style="text-align:center"><strong>CORPORATE MEMBER</strong></p></div></div></div></div><div class="row section"><div class="col-sm-6"><div class="type"><div class="text-wrapper cke_editable cke_editable_inline cke_contents_ltr cke_show_borders" id="editor42" spellcheck="false" style="position: relative;" role="textbox" aria-label="Rich Text Editor, editor42" title="Rich Text Editor, editor42" aria-describedby="cke_515" tabindex="0" ><p style="text-align:center"><br></p><p style="text-align:center"><br></p><p style="text-align:center"><br></p><p style="text-align:center"><br></p><p style="text-align:center"><br></p><p style="text-align:center">Ir. PUGUH DWI TJAHJONO</p><p style="text-align:justify">Graduated from Mechanical Engineering Bachelor, Institut Teknologi Sepuluh Nopember Surabaya in 1997. Appointed as General Manager of Corporate Secretary at PT INKA (Persero) since February 2019. Started career at PT INKA (Persero) since 1999 which previously as General Manager Human Capital in 2017 and President Director of PT INKA Multi Solution (Subsidiary of PT INKA) in 2018.</p></div></div></div><div class="col-sm-6"><div class="type"><div class="text-wrapper cke_editable cke_editable_inline cke_contents_ltr cke_show_borders" id="editor43" spellcheck="false" style="position: relative;" role="textbox" aria-label="Rich Text Editor, editor43" title="Rich Text Editor, editor43" aria-describedby="cke_566" tabindex="0" ><p style="text-align:center"><img alt="" data-cke-saved-src="/kcfinder/upload/images/Audit.jpg" src="/kcfinder/upload/images/Audit.jpg" style="height:169px; width:300px"></p><p style="text-align:center">SARMIATUN, M.M., CA.</p><p style="text-align:justify">Appointed as General Manager of Internal Audit of PT INKA (Persero) since July 2017. She graduated from Accounting of Brawijaya University and continued her Master\'s Degree in Economics and Business at Gajah Mada University. She started a career in PT INKA (Persero) since 1992 with previous position is Director of PT INKA Multi Solution which is&nbsp; subsidiary company since 2015 until 2016.</p></div></div></div></div>', '2019-05-08 06:06:40', '2019-05-08 06:06:40'),
