"textbox" aria-label="Rich Text Editor, editor4" title="Rich Text Editor, editor4" aria-describedby="cke_334" ><p style="text-align: justify;">Officially appointed as the Executive Commissioner of PT INKA (Persero) as of October 2017, he also works as the General Secretary of the Ministry of Industry. He was born in Lampung in 1959, he achieved his Bachelor Degree of State Administration in 1989 at STIA LAN RI (Administration State Academy of Indonesia), Magister Graduate School of International Development Studies in 1996 at Nagoya University and Doctoral Ph.D subject of International Cooperation Studies in 2000 from Nagoya University.<br></p></div></div></div></div><div class="row section"><div class="col-sm-4"><div class="type"><div class="text-wrapper cke_editable cke_editable_inline cke_contents_ltr cke_show_borders" id="editor5" tabindex="0" spellcheck="false" style="position: relative;" role="textbox" aria-label="Rich Text Editor, editor5" title="Rich Text Editor, editor5" aria-describedby="cke_391" ><p style="text-align: center;"><img alt="" data-cke-saved-src="/kcfinder/upload/images/Direksi%20dan%20Dekom/Brahmantyo%20web.jpg" src="/kcfinder/upload/images/Direksi%20dan%20Dekom/Brahmantyo%20web.jpg" style="width: 200px; height: 267px;"><br></p><p style="text-align:center">Ir. BRAHMANTIO ISDIJOSO, M. S.</p> </div></div></div><div class="col-sm-4"><div class="type"><div class="text-wrapper cke_editable cke_editable_inline cke_contents_ltr cke_show_borders" id="editor6" tabindex="0" spellcheck="false" style="position: relative;" role="textbox" aria-label="Rich Text Editor, editor6" title="Rich Text Editor, editor6" aria-describedby="cke_551" ><p style="text-align: center;"><img alt="" data-cke-saved-src="/kcfinder/upload/images/Direksi%20dan%20Dekom/Safri%20web.jpg" src="/kcfinder/upload/images/Direksi%20dan%20Dekom/Safri%20web.jpg" style="width: 200px; height: 267px;"><br></p><p style="text-align:center">Dr. Ir. SAFRI BURHANUDIN, DEA.</p> </div></div></div><div class="col-sm-4"><div class="type"><div class="text-wrapper cke_editable cke_editable_inline cke_contents_ltr cke_show_borders" id="editor7" tabindex="0" spellcheck="false" style="position: relative;" role="textbox" aria-label="Rich Text Editor, editor7" title="Rich Text Editor, editor7" aria-describedby="cke_711" ><p style="text-align: center;"><br></p><p style="text-align: center;"><br></p><p style="text-align: center;"><br></p><p style="text-align: center;"><br></p><p style="text-align: center;"><br></p><p style="text-align: center;"><br></p><p style="text-align: center;"><br></p><p style="text-align: center;"><br></p><p style="text-align: center;"><br></p><p style="text-align: center;">Dr. Ir. LEONARD V.H. TAMPUBOLON, MA <br></p></div></div></div></div><div class="row section"><div class="col-sm-4"><div class="type"><div class="text-wrapper cke_editable cke_editable_inline cke_contents_ltr cke_show_borders" id="editor8" tabindex="0" spellcheck="false" style="position: relative;" role="textbox" aria-label="Rich Text Editor, editor8" title="Rich Text Editor, editor8" aria-describedby="cke_767" ><p style="text-align: justify;">  Officially appointed as the Commissioner of PT INKA (Persero) as of October 2017, and he is also the Director of State Financial Risk Management due to 2 April 2015 to present. Previously he was the Chief of Fiscal Risk Management. He was born in Malang in 1965, he achieved his Master Degree in Agriculture Economics from Bogor Agricultural University in 1990.<br></p></div></div></div><div class="col-sm-4"><div class="type"><div class="text-wrapper cke_editable cke_editable_inline cke_contents_ltr cke_show_borders" id="editor9" tabindex="0" spellcheck="false" style="position: relative;" role="textbox" aria-label="Rich Text Editor, editor9" title="Rich Text Editor, editor9" aria-describedby="cke_826" ><p style="text-align: justify;">Officially appointed as the Commissioner of PT INKA (Persero) as of October 2017, he is also the Deputy IV in Human Capital Coordination Subject, Science Technology and Nautical Culture in Coordinator Ministry of Nautical Field Republic of Indonesia. He was born in Ujung Pandang in 1961, he achieved his Bachelor Degree of Geology Subject in Padjajaran University and proceeded to Universitie de Bretagne Occidentale, France in Marine Geology Subject and achieved his degree in 1994.<br></p></div></div></div><div class="col-sm-4"><div class="type"><div class="text-wrapper cke_editable cke_editable_inline cke_contents_ltr cke_show_borders" id="editor10" tabindex="0" spellcheck="false" style="position: relative;" role="textbox" aria-label="Rich Text Editor, editor10" title="Rich Text Editor, editor10" aria-describedby="cke_883" ><p>Officially appointed as the Commissioner of PT INKA (Persero) as of May 2019, he was born in Medan in 1961. He received Master Degree in Economics Development from Vanderbilt University and Doctoral Degree in Economics from Claremont Graduate University, USA. In his almost 30 years in Bappenas, Mr. Tampubolon has worked in various capacities including Director for State Finance and Director for Macroeconomics Planning. Currently he serves as Deputy Minister for Economic Affairs in Bappenas.<br></p></div></div></div></div><div class="row section"><div class="col-sm-12"><div class="type"><div class="text-wrapper cke_editable cke_editable_inline cke_contents_ltr cke_show_borders" id="editor11" tabindex="0" spellcheck="false" style="position: relative;" role="textbox" aria-label="Rich Text Editor, editor11" title="Rich Text Editor, editor11" aria-describedby="cke_949" ><p style="text-align: center;"><strong>BOARD OF DIRECTORS</strong><br></p></div></div></div></div><div class="row section"><div class="col-sm-12"><div class="type"><div class="text-wrapper cke_editable cke_editable_inline cke_contents_ltr cke_show_borders cke_focus" id="editor12" tabindex="0" spellcheck="false" style="position: relative;" role="textbox" aria-label="Rich Text Editor, editor1