 Culture in Coordinator Ministry of Nautical Field Republic of Indonesia. He was born in Ujung Pandang in 1961, he achieved his Bachelor Degree of Geology Subject in Padjajaran University and proceeded to Universitie de Bretagne Occidentale, France in Marine Geology Subject and achieved his degree in 1994.<br></p></div></div></div><div class="col-sm-4"><div class="type"><div class="text-wrapper cke_editable cke_editable_inline cke_contents_ltr cke_show_borders" id="editor10" tabindex="0" spellcheck="false" style="position: relative;" role="textbox" aria-label="Rich Text Editor, editor10" title="Rich Text Editor, editor10" aria-describedby="cke_883" ><p>Officially appointed as the Commissioner of PT INKA (Persero) as of May 2019, he was born in Medan in 1961. He received Master Degree in Economics Development from Vanderbilt University and Doctoral Degree in Economics from Claremont Graduate University, USA. In his almost 30 years in Bappenas, Mr. Tampubolon has worked in various capacities including Director for State Finance and Director for Macroeconomics Planning. Currently he serves as Deputy Minister for Economic Affairs in Bappenas.<br></p></div></div></div></div><div class="row section"><div class="col-sm-12"><div class="type"><div class="text-wrapper cke_editable cke_editable_inline cke_contents_ltr cke_show_borders" id="editor11" tabindex="0" spellcheck="false" style="position: relative;" role="textbox" aria-label="Rich Text Editor, editor11" title="Rich Text Editor, editor11" aria-describedby="cke_949" ><p style="text-align: center;"><strong>BOARD OF DIRECTORS</strong><br></p></div></div></div></div><div class="row section"><div class="col-sm-12"><div class="type"><div class="text-wrapper cke_editable cke_editable_inline cke_contents_ltr cke_show_borders" id="editor12" tabindex="0" spellcheck="false" style="position: relative;" role="textbox" aria-label="Rich Text Editor, editor12" title="Rich Text Editor, editor12" aria-describedby="cke_1005" ><p style="t