n (2015).</p><p style="text-align:justify"><br></p><p style="text-align:justify"><br></p></div></div></div><div class="col-sm-4"><div class="type"><div class="text-wrapper cke_editable cke_editable_inline cke_contents_ltr cke_show_borders" id="editor19" spellcheck="false" style="position: relative;" role="textbox" aria-label="Rich Text Editor, editor19" title="Rich Text Editor, editor19" aria-describedby="cke_994" tabindex="0" ><p style="text-align:justify">Appointed as Director of Production of PT INKA (Persero) since January 2018. He graduated from Engineering Department of Mechanical Engineering, Sepuluh November Institute of Technology Surabaya in 1992 and continued his Master\'s Degree in Engineering at Sepuluh November Institute of Technology Surabaya Department of Mechatronics in 2005. Previous history Manager of Finishing Division (2014) and General Manager of Logistics Division (2015).</p></div></div></div></div>\n		    <div class="row section"><div class="col-sm-12"><div class="type"><div class="text-wrapper cke_editable cke_editable_inline cke_contents_ltr cke_show_borders" id="editor20" tabindex="0" spellcheck="false" style="position: relative;" role="textbox" aria-label="Rich Text Editor, editor20" title="Rich Text Editor, editor20" aria-describedby="cke_1051" ><p style="text-align: center;"><strong>CORPORATE MEMBERS</strong><br></p></div></div></div></div>\n		    <div class="row section"><div class="col-sm-6"><div class="type"><div class="text-wrapper cke_editable cke_editable_inline cke_contents_ltr cke_show_borders cke_focus" id="editor21" tabindex="0" spellcheck="false" style="position: relative;" role="textbox" aria-label="Rich Text Editor, editor21" title="Rich Text Editor, editor21" aria-describedby="cke_1108" ><p style="text-align:center"><br></p><p style="text-align:center"><br></p><p style="text-align:center"><br></p><p style="text-align:center"><br></p><p style="text-align:center"><br></p><p style="text-align:center">Ir. PUGUH DWI TJAHJONO<br