m Nagoya University.</p></div></div></div></div><div class="row section"><div class="col-sm-4"><div class="type"><div class="text-wrapper cke_editable cke_editable_inline cke_contents_ltr cke_show_borders" id="editor5" spellcheck="false" style="position: relative;" role="textbox" aria-label="Rich Text Editor, editor5" title="Rich Text Editor, editor5" aria-describedby="cke_280" tabindex="0" ><p style="text-align:center"><img alt="" data-cke-saved-src="/kcfinder/upload/images/Direksi%20dan%20Dekom/Brahmantyo%20web.jpg" src="/kcfinder/upload/images/Direksi%20dan%20Dekom/Brahmantyo%20web.jpg" style="height:267px; width:200px"></p><p style="text-align:center">Ir. BRAHMANTIO ISDIJOSO, M. S.</p></div></div></div><div class="col-sm-4"><div class="type"><div class="text-wrapper cke_editable cke_editable_inline cke_contents_ltr cke_show_borders" id="editor6" spellcheck="false" style="position: relative;" role="textbox" aria-label="Rich Text Editor, editor6" title="Rich Text Editor, editor6" aria-describedby="cke_331" tabindex="0" ><p style="text-align:center"><img alt="" data-cke-saved-src="/kcfinder/upload/images/Direksi%20dan%20Dekom/Safri%20web.jpg" src="/kcfinder/upload/images/Direksi%20dan%20Dekom/Safri%20web.jpg" style="height:267px; width:200px"></p><p style="text-align:center">Dr. Ir. SAFRI BURHANUDIN, DEA.</p></div></div></div><div class="col-sm-4"><div class="type"><div class="text-wrapper cke_editable cke_editable_inline cke_contents_ltr cke_show_borders" id="editor7" spellcheck="false" style="position: relative;" role="textbox" aria-label="Rich Text Editor, editor7" title="Rich Text Editor, editor7" aria-describedby="cke_382" tabindex="0" ><p style="text-align:center"><br></p><p style="text-align:center"><br></p><p style="text-align:center"><br></p><p style="text-align:center"><br></p><p style="text-align:center"><br></p><p style="text-align:center"><br></p><p style="text-align:center"><br></p><p style="text-align:center">Dr. Ir. LEONARD V.H. TAMPUBOLON, MA</p></div></div></div></div><div class="row section"><div class="col-sm-4"><div class="type"><div class="text-wrapper cke_editable cke_editable_inline cke_contents_ltr cke_show_borders" id="editor8" spellcheck="false" style="position: relative;" role="textbox" aria-label="Rich Text Editor, editor8" title="Rich Text Editor, editor8" aria-describedby="cke_433" tabindex="0" ><p style="text-align:justify">Officially appointed as the Commissioner of PT INKA (Persero) as of October 2017, and he is also the Director of State Financial Risk Management due to 2 April 2015 to present. Previously he was the Chief of Fiscal Risk Management. He was born in Malang in 1965, he achieved his Master Degree in Agriculture Economics from Bogor Agricultural University in 1990.</p></div></div></div><div class="col-sm-4"><div class="type"><div class="text-wrapper cke_editable cke_editable_inline cke_contents_ltr cke_show_borders" id="editor9" spellcheck="false" style="position: relative;" role="textbox" aria-label="Rich Text Editor, editor9" title="Rich Text Editor, editor9" aria-describedby="cke_484" tabindex="0" ><p style="text-align:justify">Officially appointed as the Commissioner of PT INKA (Persero) as of October 2017, he is also the Deputy IV in Human Capital Coordination Subject, Science Technology and Nautical Culture in Coordinator Ministry of Nautical Field Republic of Indonesia. He was born in Ujung Pandang in 1961, he achieved his Bachelor Degree of Geology Subject in Padjajaran University and proceeded to Universitie de Bretagne Occidentale, France in Marine Geology Subject and achieved his degree in 1994.</p></div></div></div><div class="col-sm-4"><div class="type"><div class="text-wrapper cke_editable cke_editable_inline cke_contents_ltr cke_show_borders" id="editor10" spellcheck="false" style="position: relative;" role="textbox" aria-label="Rich Text Editor, editor10" title="Rich Text Editor, editor10" aria-describedby="cke_535" tabindex="0" ><p style="text-align:justify">Officially appointed as the Commissioner of PT INKA (Persero) as of May 2019, he was born in Medan in 1961. He received Master Degree in Economics Development from Vanderbilt University and Doctoral Degree in Economics from Claremont Graduate University, USA. In his almost 30 years in Bappenas, Mr. Tampubolon has worked in various capacities including Director for State Finance and Director for Macroeconomics Planning. Currently he serves as Deputy Minister for Economic Affairs in Bappenas.</p></div></div></div></div><div class="row section"><div class="col-sm-12"><div class="type"><div class="text-wrapper cke_editable cke_editable_inline cke_contents_ltr cke_show_borders" id="editor11" spellcheck="false" style="position: relative;" role="textbox" aria-label="Rich Text Editor, editor11" title="Rich Text Editor, editor11" aria-describedby="cke_586" tabindex="0" ><p style="text-align:center"><strong>BOARD OF DIRECTORS</strong><br></p></div></div></div></div><div class="row section"><div class="col-sm-12"><div class="type"><div class="text-wrapper cke_editable cke_editable_inline cke_contents_ltr cke_show_borders" id="editor12" spellcheck="false" style="position: relative;" role="textbox" aria-label="Rich Text Editor, editor12" title="Rich Text Editor, editor12" aria-describedby="cke_637" tabindex="0" ><p style="text-align:center"><img alt="" data-cke-saved-src="/kcfinder/upload/images/Slider/BOC%20BOD/Dirut.jpg" src="/kcfinder/upload/images/Slider/BOC%20BOD/Dirut.jpg" style="height:169px; width:300px"></p><p style="text-align:center">Ir. BUDI NOVIANTORO</p></div></div></div></div><div class="row section"><div class="col-sm-12"><div class="type"><div class="text-wrapper cke_editable cke_editable_inline cke_contents_ltr cke_show_borders" id="editor13" spellcheck="false" style="position: relative;" role="textbox" aria-label="Rich Text Editor, editor13" title="Rich Text Editor, editor13" aria-describedby="cke_688" tabindex="0" ><p style="text-align:justify">Appointed as President Director of PT INKA (Persero) since January 2018. He is a graduate of Civil Engineering. Department of Hydraulics, Sepuluh November Institute of Technology Surabaya in 1985. Previous history of Director of Logistics and Business Development of PT KAI (2014) and Ad Interim President Director of PT KAI (2018).</p></div></div></div></div><div class="row section"><div class="col-sm-4"><div class="type"><div class="text-wrapper cke_editable cke_editable_inline cke_contents_ltr cke_show_borders" id="editor14" spellcheck="false" style="position: relative;" role="textbox" aria-label="Rich Text Editor, editor14" title="Rich Text Editor, editor14" aria-describedby="cke_739" tabindex="0" ><p style="text-align:center"><img alt="" data-cke-saved-src="/kcfinder/upload/images/Slider/BOC%20BOD/Dirkeu.jpg" src="/kcfinder/upload/images/Slider/BOC%20BOD/Dirkeu.jpg" style="height:169px; width:300px"></p><p style="text-align:center">Ir. MARDIANNUS PRAMUDYA, M.M.T.</p></div></div></div><div class="col-sm-4"><div class="type"><div class="text-wrapper cke_editable cke_editable_inline cke_contents_ltr cke_show_borders" id="editor15" spellcheck="false" style="position: relative;" role="textbox" aria-label="Rich Text Editor, editor15" title="Rich Text Editor, editor15" aria-describedby="cke_790" tabindex="0" ><p style="text-align:center"><img alt="" data-cke-saved-src="/kcfinder/upload/images/Slider/BOC%20BOD/Dirtek.jpg" src="/kcfinder/upload/images/Slider/BOC%20BOD/Dirtek.jpg" style="height:169px; width:300px"></p><p style="text-align:center">Ir. AGUNG SEDAJU, M.T.</p></div></div></div><div class="col-sm-4"><div class="type"><div class="text-wrapper cke_editable cke_editable_inline cke_contents_ltr cke_show_borders" id="editor16" spellcheck="false" style="position: relative;" role="textbox" aria-label="Rich Text Editor, editor16" title="Rich Text Editor, editor16" aria-describedby="cke_841" tabindex="0" ><p style="text-align:center"><img alt="" data-cke-saved-src="/kcfinder/upload/images/Slider/BOC%20BOD/Dirprod.jpg" src="/kcfinder/upload/images/Slider/BOC%20BOD/Dirprod.jpg" style="height:169px; width:300px"></p><p style="text-align:center">Ir. BAYU WASKITO SUDADI, M.T.</p></div></div></div></div><div class="row section"><div class="col-sm-4"><div class="type"><div class="text-wrapper cke_editable cke_editable_inline cke_contents_ltr cke_show_borders" id="editor17" spellcheck="false" style="position: relative;" role="textbox" aria-label="Rich Text Editor, editor17" title="Rich Text Editor, editor17" aria-describedby="cke_892" tabindex="0" ><p style="text-align: justify;">Appointed as Finance &amp; Human Resources Director of PT INKA (Persero) since August 2018. He started his career at PT INKA (Persero) since 1995 and served as General Manager of the Finance Division in 2014 and General Manager of Logistics Division in 2018. He graduated from the Brawijaya University, Mechanical Engineering Department in 1993. Then continued his master\'s degree at Sepuluh November Institute of Technology Surabaya Department of Project Management in 2005.<br></p></div></div></div><div class="col-sm-4"><div class="type"><div class="text-wrapper cke_editable cke_editable_inline cke_contents_ltr cke_show_borders" id="editor18" spellcheck="false" style="position: relative;" role="textbox" aria-label="Rich Text Editor, editor18" title="Rich Text Editor, editor18" aria-describedby="cke_943" tabindex="0" ><p style="text-align:justify">Appointed as Technology and Commercial Director of PT INKA (Persero) since January 2018. He holds a Bachelor degree in Bandung Institute of Technology Department of Physical Engineering in 1995 and continued his Master\'s Degree in Engineering at Sepuluh November Institute of Technology Surabaya Department of Electrical Engineering in 2006. He pioneered a career in PT INKA (Persero) since 1996 and served as General Manager of Human Capital Division (2012), General Manager of Logistic Division (2014), and General Manager of Technology Division (2015).</p><p style="text-align:justify"><br></p><p style="text-align:justify"><br></p></div></div></div><div class="col-sm-4"><div class="type"><div class="text-wrapper cke_editable cke_editable_inline cke_contents_ltr cke_show_borders" id="editor19" spellcheck="false" style="position: relative;" role="textbox" aria-label="Rich Text Editor, editor19" title="Rich Text Editor, editor19" aria-describedby="cke_994" tabindex="0" ><p style="text-align:justify">Appointed as Director of Production of PT INKA (Persero) since January 2018. He graduated from Engineering Department of Mechanical Engineering, Sepuluh November Institute of Technology Surabaya in 1992 and continued his Master\'s Degree in Engineering at Sepuluh November Institute of Technology Surabaya Department of Mechatronics in 2005. Previous history Manager of Finishing Division (2014) and General Manager of Logistics Division (2015).</p></div></div></div></div>\n		    <div class="row section"><div class="col-sm-12"><div class="type"><div class="text-wrapper cke_editable cke_editable_inline cke_contents_ltr cke_show_borders" id="editor20" tabindex="0" spellcheck="false" style="position: relative;" role="textbox" aria-label="Rich Text Editor, editor20" title="Rich Text Editor, editor20" aria-describedby="cke_1051" ><p style="text-align: center;"><strong>CORPORATE MEMBERS</strong><br></p></div></div></div></div>\n		    <div class="row section"><div class="col-sm-6"><div class="type"><div class="text-wrapper cke_editable cke_editable_inline cke_contents_ltr cke_show_borders" id="editor21" tabindex="0" spellcheck="false" style="position: relative;" role="textbox" aria-label="Rich Text Editor, editor21" title="Rich Text Editor, editor21" aria-describedby="cke_1108" ><p style="text-align:center"><br></p><p style="text-align:center"><br></p><p style="text-align:center"><br></p><p style="text-align:center"><br></p><p style="text-align:center"><br></p><p style="text-align:center">Ir. PUGUH DWI TJAHJONO<br></p> </div></div></div><div class="col-sm-6"><div class="type"><div class="text-wrapper cke_editable cke_editable_inline cke_contents_ltr cke_show_borders" id="editor22" tabindex="0" spellcheck="false" style="position: relative;" role="textbox" aria-label="Rich Text Editor, editor22" title="Rich Text Editor, editor22" aria-describedby="cke_1163" ><p style="text-align: center;"><img alt="" data-cke-saved-src="/kcfinder/upload/images/Slider/BOC%20BOD/Audit.jpg" src="/kcfinder/upload/images/Slider/BOC%20BOD/Audit.jpg" style="width: 300px; height: 169px;"><br></p><p style="text-align:center">SARMIATUN, MM., CA.</p> </div></div></div></div><div class="row section"><div class="col-sm-6"><div class="type"><div class="text-wrapper cke_editable cke_editable_inline cke_contents_ltr cke_show_borders cke_focus" id="editor24" tabindex="0" spellcheck="false" style="position: relative;" role="textbox" aria-label="Rich Text Editor, editor24" title="Rich Text Editor, editor24" aria-describedby="cke_1381" ><p><br></p></div></div></div><div class="col-sm-6"><div class="type"><div class="text-wrapper cke_editable cke_editable_inline cke_contents_ltr cke_show_borders" id="editor23" tabindex="0" spellcheck="false" style="position: relative;" role="textbox" aria-label="Rich Text Editor, editor23" title="Rich Text Editor, editor23" aria-describedby="cke_1324" ><p style="text-align: justify;"> Appointed as General Manager of Internal Audit of PT INKA (Persero) since July 2017. She graduated from Accounting of Brawijaya University and continued her Master\'s Degree in Economics and Business at Gajah Mada University. She started a career in PT INKA (Persero) since 1992. <br></p></div></div></div></div>', '2019-05-13 09:09:22', '2019-05-13 09:09:22'),
	(3043748, '<div class="row section"><div class="col-sm-12"><div class="type"><div class="image-wrapper"><img src="/kcfinder/upload/images/2019/Mei%202019/WhatsApp%20Image%202019-05-13%20at%2010.59.16%20AM.jpeg"><div class="image-caption" ></div></div></div></div></div><div class="row section"><div class="col-sm-12"><div class="type"><div class="text-wrapper cke_editable cke_editable_inline cke_contents_ltr cke_show_borders cke_focus" id="editor1" tabindex="0" spellcheck="false" style="position: relative;" role="textbox" aria-label="Rich Text Editor, editor1" title="Rich Text Editor, editor1" aria-describedby="cke_59" ><p style="text-align: justify;">PT INKA (Persero) menyelenggarakan mudik gratis bagi masyarakat umum dengan beberapa kota tujuan pilihan. Kegiatan mudik gratis ini merupakan program yang digagas oleh Kementerian BUMN kepada seluruh perusahaan BUMN untuk memfasilitasi masyarakat agar dapat mudik dengan aman dan nyaman ke kampung halamannya. Informasi selengkapnya dapat mengakses <em>link </em><a data-cke-saved-href="http://mudik.inka.co.id" href="http://mudik.inka.co.id">mudik.inka.co.id</a><br>Selamat mudik !!<br></p></div></div></div></div>', '2019-05-15 09:14:25', '2019-05-15 09:14:25'),
	(6396347, '<div class="row section"><div class="col-sm-12"><div class="type"><div title="Rich Text Editor, editor2" class="text-wrapper cke_editable cke_editable_inline cke_contents_ltr cke_show_borders" id="editor2" role="textbox" aria-describedby="cke_67" style="position: relative;" spellcheck="false" aria-label="Rich Text Editor, editor2" data-gramm_editor="true" data-gramm="true" data-gramm_id="d7234ea7-494b-e6b9-e90e-cfb9b2738c42" tabindex="0" ><p style="text-align:center"><strong><span style="font-size:medium">PENGUMUMAN PELELANGAN </span></strong><br></p><p style="text-align:center"><strong>PEKERJAAN JASA PENGIRIMAN 186 CAR LRT JABODEBEK</strong><br></p><p style="text-align:center"><strong>Dari PT INKA (Persero)-Madiun Menuju Depo LRT Jabodebek</strong><br></p><p style="text-align:center"><strong>Tahun 2019 - 2020</strong><br></p></div><grammarly-btn><div class="_1BN1N Kzi1t MoE_1 _2DJZN" style="z-index: 2; transform: translate(682.793px, 101.25px);"><div class="_1HjH7"><div title="Protected by Grammarly" class="_3qe6h">&nbsp;</div></div></div></grammarly-btn></div></div></div>\n		    <div class="row section"><div class="col-sm-12"><div class="type"><div title="Rich Text Editor, editor3" class="text-wrapper cke_editable cke_editable_inline cke_contents_ltr cke_show_borders cke_focus" id="editor3" role="textbox" aria-describedby="cke_118" style="position: relative;" spellcheck="false" aria-label="Rich Text Editor, editor3" data-gramm_editor="true" data-gramm="true" data-gramm_id="0f855674-7107-68b8-2d07-8b3297455498" tabindex="0" ><p style="text-align: justify;"><strong>1. PAKET PEKERJAAN</strong><br></p><p style="text-align:justify">Departemen Pengadaan Jasa Produksi Divisi Logistik - PT Industri Kereta Api (Persero) akan melaksanakan Pelelangan dengan Pascakualifikasi untuk <strong>Pekerjaan Jasa Pengiriman 186 Car LRT JABODEBEK</strong> dari PT Industri Kereta Api (Persero), Madiun menuju Depo <em>Light Rail Transit&nbsp; </em>(LRT) Jabodebek atau tempat penyerahan di Jabodebek sesuai dengan arahan PT Industri Kereta Api (Persero). <strong>Kualifikasi pengiriman terlampir</strong>.<br></p><p style="text-align:justify"><br></p><p style="text-align:justify"><strong>2. PENDAFTARAN </strong><br></p><p style="text-align:justify">Bagi Peserta atau Penyedia yang berminat mengikuti Pelelangan tersebut, dapat mendaftarkan perusahaannya dengan ketentuan sebagai berikut : <br></p><p>a. Pendaftaran dilakukansecara elektronik dengan menggunakan akun email perusahaan Peserta.<br></p><p>b. Pendaftaran dilakukan dengan meng-<em>upload </em>dokumen <strong>terlampir.</strong><strong></strong><br></p><p><strong></strong>c. Upload dokumen terkait pada poin b melalui Email : <a data-cke-saved-href="http://pengadaan.jasa@inka.co.id" href="http://pengadaan.jasa@inka.co.id">pengadaan.jasa@inka.co.id</a> dan cc : <a data-cke-saved-href="http://pjplogisik@gmail.com" href="http://pjplogisik@gmail.com">pjplogisik@gmail.com</a> ditujukan kepada :<br></p><ul><li><p style="text-align:justify"><strong>Pelaksana Pelelangan Jasa Pengiriman 186 Car LRT JABODEBEK</strong><br></p><p style="text-align:justify">Departemen Pengadaan Jasa Produksi Divisi Logistik<br></p><p style="text-align:justify">PT Industri Kereta Api (Persero)<br></p></li></ul><p><strong><em></em></strong>d. Batas waktu pendaftaran secara elektronik adalah sejak pengumuman pelelangan ini sampai paling lambat 22 Mei 2019 pukul 11.00 WIB (mengacu pada waktu yang ditunjukkan oleh TELKOM 103)<br></p><p><br></p><p><br></p><p><br></p><p><br></p><ol><li style="text-align:justify">Hasil prakualifkasi akan disampaikan melalui pengumuman <em>website </em>atau dikirimkan kepada masing-masing pendaftar melalui <em>e-mail </em>paling lambat tanggal 02 November 2018 (harap menggunakan alamat <em>e-mail </em>perusahaan).<br></li><li style="text-align:justify">Akan dilakukan evaluasi atas dokumen prakualifikasi yang masuk, dan akan ditetapkan minimal 3 (tiga) peserta prakualifikasi yang dinyatakan lolos untuk mengikuti tahapan selanjutnya. Apabila jumlah peserta yang mendaftar atau yang lolos&nbsp; prakualifikasi kurang dari 3 (tiga) maka proses Pelelangan Ulang dinyatakan GAGAL dan untuk selanjutnya akan dilakukan pemilihan/penunjukan langsung.</li><li style="text-align:justify">Peserta yang mengundurkan diri atau peserta tidak mengikuti proses Pelelangan Ulang selanjutnya karena sebab yang tidak dapat dibenarkan, akan dikenakan sanksi berupa <em>blacklist</em> selama 2 (dua) tahun dan sanksi lain sesuai peraturan dan ketentuan yang berlaku di PT Industri Kereta Api (Persero).</li><li style="text-align:justify">Hanya rekanan yang sanggup dan mampu memenuhi persyaratan prakualifikasi yang diundang dalam lelang ini.</li><li style="text-align:justify">Untuk memudahkan proses pengecekan kelengkapan Dokumen bagi Calon Peserta Pelelangan Ulang, Pelaksana Pelelangan Ulang menyediakan <em>Check Sheet</em> pada <strong>Contoh Lampiran G </strong>yang dapat diunduh dan disertakan sebagai kelengkapan dokumen prakualifikasi.</li></ol><p style="text-align:justify"><br></p><p style="text-align:right">Madiun, 22 Oktober 2018</p><p style="text-align:justify"><br></p><p style="text-align:right">Tim Pelaksana Pelelangan Ulang</p><p style="text-align:right">Pekerjaan Jasa Pengiriman 200 Kereta</p><p style="text-align:right">Bangladesh (MG) dan <em>Capital Spares</em></p><p style="text-align:right">PT Industri Kereta Api (Persero)</p></div><grammarly-btn><div class="_1BN1N Kzi1t MoE_1 _2DJZN" style="z-index: 2; transform: translate(677.793px, 1039px);"><div class="_1HjH7"><div title="Protected by Grammarly" class="_3qe6h">&nbsp;</div></div></div></grammarly-btn></div></div></div>\n		    <div class="row section"><div class="col-sm-12"><div class="type"><div title="Rich Text Editor, editor4" class="text-wrapper cke_editable cke_editable_inline cke_contents_ltr cke_show_borders" id="editor4" role="textbox" aria-describedby="cke_169" style="position: relative;" spellcheck="false" ari