ially appointed as the Commissioner of PT INKA (Persero) as of May 2019, he was born in Medan in 1961. He received Master Degree in Economics Development from Vanderbilt University and Doctoral Degree in Economics from Claremont Graduate University, USA. In his almost 30 years in Bappenas, Mr. Tampubolon has worked in various capacities including Director for State Finance and Director for Macroeconomics Planning. Currently he serves as Deputy Minister for Economic Affairs in Bappenas.</p></div></div></div></div><div class="row section"><div class="col-sm-12"><div class="type"><div class="text-wrapper cke_editable cke_editable_inline cke_contents_ltr cke_show_borders" id="editor11" spellcheck="false" style="position: relative;" role="textbox" aria-label="Rich Text Editor, editor11" title="Rich Text Editor, editor11" aria-describedby="cke_616"  tabindex="0"><p style="text-align:center"><strong>BOARD OF DIRECTORS</strong></p></div></div></div></div><div class="row section"><div class="col-sm-12"><div class="type"><div class="text-wrapper cke_editable cke_editable_inline cke_contents_ltr cke_show_borders" id="editor12" spellcheck="false" style="position: relative;" role="textbox" aria-label="Rich Text Editor, editor12" title="Rich Text Editor, editor12" aria-describedby="cke_668"  tabindex="0"><p style="text-align:center"><img alt="" data-cke-saved-src="/kcfinder/upload/images/2020/Budi%20Noviantoro_.jpg" src="/kcfinder/upload/images/2020/Budi%20Noviantoro_.jpg" style="height: 209px; width: 200px;"></p><p style="text-align:center">Ir. BUDI NOVIANTORO</p></div></div></div></div><div class="row section"><div class="col-sm-12"><div class="type"><div class="text-wrapper cke_editable cke_editable_inline cke_contents_ltr cke_show_borders" id="editor13" spellcheck="false" style="position: relative;" role="textbox" aria-label="Rich Text Editor, editor13" title="Rich Text Editor, editor13" aria-describedby="cke_720"  tabindex="0"><p style="text-align:justify">Appointed as President Director of PT INKA (Persero) since January 2018. He is a graduate of Civil Engineering. Department of Hydraulics, Sepuluh November Institute of Technology Surabaya in 1985. Previous history of Director of Logistics and Business Development of PT KAI (2014) and Ad Interim President Director of PT KAI (2018).</p></div></div></div></div><div class="row section"><div class="col-sm-4"><div class="type"><div class="text-wrapper cke_editable cke_editable_inline cke_contents_ltr cke_show_borders" id="editor14" spellcheck="false" style="position: relative;" role="textbox" aria-label="Rich Text Editor, editor14" title="Rich Text Editor, editor14" aria-describedby="cke_772"  tabindex="0"><p style="text-align:center"><img alt="" data-cke-saved-src="/kcfinder/upload/images/2020/Mardiannus%20Pramudya%20closeup.jpg" src="/kcfinder/upload/images/2020/Mardiannus%20Pramudya%20closeup.jpg" style="height: 200px; width: 200px;"></p><p style="text-align:center">Ir. MARDIANNUS PRAMUDYA, M.M.T.</p></div></div></div><div class="col-sm-4"><div class="type"><div class="text-wrapper cke_editable cke_editable_inline cke_contents_ltr cke_show_borders" id="editor15" spellcheck="false" style="position: relative;" role="textbox" aria-label="Rich Text Editor, editor15" title="Rich Text Editor, editor15" aria-describedby="cke_824"  tabindex="0"><p style="text-align:center"><img alt="" data-cke-saved-src="/kcfinder/upload/images/2020/Agung%20Sedaju%20closeup.jpg" src="/kcfinder/upload/images/2020/Agung%20Sedaju%20closeup.jpg" style="height: 207px; width: 200px;"></p><p style="text-align:center">Ir. AGUNG SEDAJU, M.T.</p></div></div></div><div class="col-sm-4"><div class="type"><div class="text-wrapper cke_editable cke_editable_inline cke_contents_ltr cke_show_borders cke_focus" id="editor16" spellcheck="false" style="position: relative;" role="textbox" aria-label="Rich Text Editor, editor16" title="Rich Text Editor, editor16" aria-describedby="cke_876"  tabindex="0"><p style="text-align:center">