tic Division (2014), and General Manager of Technology Division (2015).</p><p style="text-align:justify"><br></p><p style="text-align:justify"><br></p></div></div></div><div class="col-sm-4"><div class="type"><div class="text-wrapper cke_editable cke_editable_inline cke_contents_ltr cke_show_borders" id="editor19" spellcheck="false" style="position: relative;" role="textbox" aria-label="Rich Text Editor, editor19" title="Rich Text Editor, editor19" aria-describedby="cke_1032"  tabindex="0"><p style="text-align:justify">Appointed as Director of Production of PT INKA (Persero) since January 2018. He graduated from Engineering Department of Mechanical Engineering, Sepuluh November Institute of Technology Surabaya in 1992 and continued his Master\'s Degree in Engineering at Sepuluh November Institute of Technology Surabaya Department of Mechatronics in 2005. Previous history Manager of Finishing Division (2014) and General Manager of Logistics Division (2015).</p></div></div></div></div>\n		    <div class="row section"><div class="col-sm-12"><div class="type"><div class="text-wrapper cke_editable cke_editable_inline cke_contents_ltr cke_show_borders" id="editor20" spellcheck="false" style="position: relative;" role="textbox" aria-label="Rich Text Editor, editor20" title="Rich Text Editor, editor20" aria-describedby="cke_1084"  tabindex="0"><p style="text-align:center"><strong>CORPORATE MEMBERS</strong></p></div></div></div></div>\n		    <div class="row section"><div class="col-sm-6"><div class="type"><div class="text-wrapper cke_editable cke_editable_inline cke_contents_ltr cke_show_borders" id="editor21" spellcheck="false" style="position: relative;" role="textbox" aria-label="Rich Text Editor, editor21" title="Rich Text Editor, editor21" aria-describedby="cke_1136"  tabindex="0"><p style="text-align:center">​​​​​​​<img alt="" data-cke-saved-src="/kcfinder/upload/images/2020/P.jpg" src="/kcfinder/upload/images/2020/P.jpg" style="width: 300px; height: 169px;"><br></p><p style="text-align:center">Ir. PUGUH DWI TJAHJONO</p></div></div></div><div class="col-sm-6"><div class="type"><div class="text-wrapper cke_editable cke_editable_inline cke_contents_ltr cke_show_borders" id="editor22" spellcheck="false" style="position: relative;" role="textbox" aria-label="Rich Text Editor, editor22" title="Rich Text Editor, editor22" aria-describedby="cke_1188"  tabindex="0"><p style="text-align:center"><img alt="" data-cke-saved-src="/kcfinder/upload/images/2020/M.jpg" src="/kcfinder/upload/images/2020/M.jpg" style="height:169px; width:300px"></p><p style="text-align:center">SARMIATUN, MM., CA.</p></div></div></div></div><div class="row section"><div class="col-sm-6"><div class="type"><div class="text-wrapper cke_editable cke_editable_inline cke_contents_ltr cke_focus cke_show_borders" id="editor24" spellcheck="false" style="position: relative;" role="textbox" aria-label="Rich Text Editor, editor24" title="Rich Text Editor, editor24" aria-describedby="cke_1292"  tabindex="0"><p style="text-align:justify">Appointed as General Manager of Corporate Secretary of PT INKA (Persero) since February 2019. He graduated from Mechanical Engineering, Sepuluh November Institute of Technology Surabaya in 1997. He pioneered career at PT INKA (Persero) since 1999 which previously served as General Manager Human Capital in 2017 and as President Director of PT INKA Multi Solution (Subsidiary of PT INKA) Ad Interim in 2018.</p><p><br></p></div></div></div><div class="col-sm-6"><div class="type"><div class="text-wrapper cke_editable cke_editable_inline cke_contents_ltr cke_show_borders" id="editor23" spellcheck="false" style="position: relative;" role="textbox" aria-label="Rich Text Editor, editor23" title="Rich Text Editor, editor23" aria-describedby="cke_1240"  tabindex="0"><p style="text-align:justify">Appointed as General Manager of Internal Audit of PT INKA (Persero) since July 2017. She graduated from Accounting of Brawijaya University and continued her Master\