	(3223519, '<div class="row section"><div class="col-sm-12"><div class="type"><div class="image-wrapper"><img src="/kcfinder/upload/images/Subsidiary.jpg"><div class="image-caption" ><br></div></div></div></div></div><div class="row section"><div class="col-sm-12"><div class="type"><div title="Rich Text Editor, editor4" class="text-wrapper cke_editable cke_editable_inline cke_contents_ltr cke_focus cke_show_borders" id="editor4" role="textbox" aria-describedby="cke_67" style="position: relative;" spellcheck="false" aria-label="Rich Text Editor, editor4" tabindex="0" ><p><span style="font-size:14px">PT INKA establishes two subsidiary companies, they are <a href="http://inkamultisolusi.co.id/" data-cke-saved-href="http://inkamultisolusi.co.id/">PT Inka Multi Solusi </a>and <a href="http://www.rekaindo.net/" data-cke-saved-href="http://www.rekaindo.net/">PT Rekaindo Global Jasa</a>.</span></p></div></div></div></div><div class="row section"><div class="col-sm-12"><div class="type"><div class="image-wrapper"><img src="/kcfinder/upload/images/Logo-IMS3.png"><div class="image-caption" ><i>PT Inka Multi Solusi</i></div></div></div></div></div><div class="row section"><div class="col-sm-12"><div class="type"><div title="Rich Text Editor, editor5" class="text-wrapper cke_editable cke_editable_inline cke_contents_ltr cke_show_borders" id="editor5" role="textbox" aria-describedby="cke_118" style="position: relative;" spellcheck="false" aria-label="Rich Text Editor, editor5" tabindex="0" ><p style="text-align:justify"><span style="font-size:14px">PT Inka Multi Solusi establishes since 2009, based on deeds Maria Liliana Handojo, S.H.&nbsp; No. 66 December 23, 2009. Share certificate : PT INKA (Persero) 45.3%, Kopinka 44.9%, and the rest is Yayasan Keluarga Besar INKA 9.8%. It is located on Jl. M.T. Haryono No. 103 Madiun. The business competences are chartering services providing or sub-contracting to support the finishing of INKA projects.</span></p><p style="text-align:justify